On <http://example.com|example.com> you could do a script that checks `request.geoipCountry` and redirects if it matches one of the country codes in your list.
```&lt;script&gt;
  var countries = ['sv-se', 'no']
  if (countries.includes('{{ request.geoipCountry }}')) {
    document.location = '<https://example.com/>{{ request.geoipCountry }}';
  }
&lt;/script&gt;```
